---
// src/components/ProductsSection.astro
---
<section class="py-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-violet-700">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Productos Destacados</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/producto1.jpg" alt="Bata Quirúrgica Desechable" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Bata Quirúrgica Desechable</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Bata quirúrgica de alta calidad, impermeable y resistente a fluidos.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="inline-block bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-md">Ver Detalles</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/producto2.jpg" alt="Ropa de Paciente" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Ropa de Paciente</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Cómoda y suave ropa de paciente para una estancia confortable en el hospital.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="inline-block bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-md">Ver Detalles</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/producto3.jpg" alt="Uniforme Médico" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Uniforme Médico</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Uniformes médicos profesionales y duraderos para diferentes especialidades.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="inline-block bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-md">Ver Detalles</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>